cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and dependency parsing, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of neural networks and deep learning techniques suggests that it could also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of contextualized word embeddings, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks as well, indicating a possible connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
